# Cumulative Count Implementation Plan

## Goal
Implement a cumulative count for habits that persists even when the daily progress is reset.

## Proposed Changes

### [MODIFY] [App.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/src/App.jsx)
- **State Initialization:**
  - When loading `habits` from local storage or defaults, ensure each habit has a `count` property.
  - If `count` is missing, initialize it to `history.length`.
- **[toggleHabit](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/src/App.jsx#110-126) Function:**
  - Logic update:
    - If completing (adding `today`): Increment `count` (`count + 1`).
    - If un-completing (removing `today`): Decrement `count` (`Math.max(0, count - 1)`).
- **[resetDailyProgress](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/src/App.jsx#149-161) Function:**
  - No changes needed to `count`. It calculates based on `history` filter, so `count` remains untouched, effectively preserving the "done" status stats-wise.

### [MODIFY] [Stats.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/src/Stats.jsx)
- **Cumulative Stat:** Update `totalHistoryCount` to sum `habit.count` instead of `habit.history.length`.
- **Total Status List:** Update the list rendering to display `habit.count` instead of `habit.history.length`.

## Verification Plan
- **Manual Verification:**
  - Check a habit -> Count increases.
  - Reset Day -> Count stays same.
  - Check same habit again -> Count increases (should be +1 from before reset).
